**Bitcoin Watch** provided a real-time snapshot of a number of data attributes relating to Bitcoin.  features of the service are now avaialable on [[Bitcoin_Charts]].

Data Attributes

* Economic size (e.g., total bitcoins generated and value)
* Transaction statistics
* Exchange rates and exchange data.

##History

The site operated from at least 2010 through March 27, 2011 when the founder of [[Bitcoin_Charts]] announced the service had changed owners (2.1)

